data.title: Günther Johannes Paetsch
data.meta_description: Günther Johannes Paetsch, a native of Germany, was a cellist and co-founder of the Paetsch Family Chamber Music Ensemble in Colorado Springs, Colorado, United States. He is the husband of violinist Priscilla Paetsch and the father of their seven children.
